    "page_no": 15,
    "unit_id": "p15_g05",
    "unit_mode": "semantic_group",
    "slot_count": 3,
    "source_text": "我們從2020年下半年起，透過友邦保險在新加坡和越南的業務作為兩個試點業務單位，展開塑造一個轉型機構的\n旅程。初步成果已實現更簡化、更以客為本的營運模式，我們亦推行靈活的工作方式，設立多個跨職能的專家團\n隊。我們計劃在這些試點業務內進行試驗和學習，然後將「未來的組織」項目擴展至其他業務。",
    "current_translation": "Since the second half of 2020, we have embarked on a journey to shape a transformational organization through AIA's businesses in Singapore and Vietnam as two pilot business units. Initial results have delivered a more streamlined and customer-centric operating model, and we have implemented flexible working arrangements and established multiple cross-functional expert teams. We plan to experiment and learn within these pilot businesses before expanding the \"Organisation of the Future\" programme to other operations."
  },
